  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Raise awareness on school management and facilitate SMC for representing the whole community.\r\n    School Improvement Plan (SIP) development and implementation\r\n    Improved training for school/SMC for community mobilization to increase enrollment and reduce dropout.\r\n    Support and facilitate DEO to clarify district educational problems through analyzing SIP and to support disadvantaged schools technically and financially.\r\n    Strengthen the network of stakeholders in education (VDC, DDC, DEC, DEO and other relevant stakeholders)\r\n    Suggest alternative policies to MOES/DOE to achieve minimum quality of education."
    },
